{"type":"message","id":"9bad5f11","parentId":"d0324119","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:34:08.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! I can see the runs. Let me analyze:\n\n**Current run `vqm9aldo` (running):**\n- Phase 1 results\n- `train/accuracy: 0.95` — very good!\n- `train/blocked_frac: 0` — NO blocking at all!\n- `train/write_frac: 0.105` — 10.5% writes\n- `train/read_frac: 0.105` — 10.5% reads\n- `train/skip_frac: 0.789` — 78.9% skips\n- `train/tau: 0.962` — still in annealing (gumbel softmax)\n\n\n- `train/route_loss: 1.06` and `train/div_loss: 0.062` — the model has learned to route with decent diversity\n- `train/answer_loss: 0.546` — the fractured head is clearly functioning since there's no blocking\n\nThe previous collapsed runs like `o03t8c13` and `wiut5ita` show the classic pattern: 71% blocking, zero accuracy, 28.9% write fraction. But this current run is completely different — zero blocking, high accuracy, and a healthy routing distribution across skips, reads, and writes. This is a Phase 1 run, and the fractured head architecture appears to be solving the blocking problem that plagued earlier attempts.\n\nNow I need to dig into the training timeline to see where Phase 2 actually starts and what happens after that.","thinkingSignature":"00cda46502014cd56e86fba9a7552b64c1a35b200fa376b6188843df8ffc8674"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it. Here's what I see:\n\n**Current run `vqm9aldo` (running, Phase 1):**\n- `acc=0.950` — excellent\n- `blocked_frac=0.000` — **zero blocking** — the fractured head is working\n- `write_frac=0.105, read_frac=0.105, skip_frac=0.789` — healthy routing distribution\n- `tau=0.962` — still annealing (Phase 1 hasn't finished)\n- `div_loss=0.062` — diversity regularizer is active\n\n**Previous collapsed runs** (`o03t8c13`, `wiut5ita`, `22cpqp1o`) all show the same failure mode: `blocked_frac=0.71`, `acc=0.0`, `write_frac=0.289` — WRITE exhaustion every time.\n\nThe fractured head fix is clearly working — **zero blocking in Phase 1**. That's a real win.\n\nHow far into the run are you? It looks like Phase 1 hasn't finished yet (tau still 0.96). Once it hits tau→0 and transitions to Phase 2 with DAgger, that's the real test."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":87883,"output":579,"cacheRead":14175,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102637,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774362833216}}
