{"type":"message","id":"04b7b937","parentId":"af401c68","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:35:58.922Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to add:\n1. Before Phase 1 loop: check for checkpoint, load if exists, skip Phase 1\n2. After Phase 1: save checkpoint\n\nThe checkpoint should save: model state, optimizer state, trainer._ep_count, and rng state.\n\nLet me add this at the beginning of the training cell (before Phase 1 for loop) and after Phase 1 done print.","thinkingSignature":"164c4f5c66a1a8c106791bc93c1b07bfd817a6545f20b6cce7ff4bd036f07dfd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aps3zxvhl46w_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\add_checkpoint.py","content":"import json, sys\n\nwith open(r'C:\\dev\\notebooks\\SRMoE_Training.ipynb', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    nb = json.load(f)\n\nlines = nb['cells'][10]['source']\n\n# Find \"Phase 1 done\" line to add checkpoint save after it\np1_done_line = None\nfor i, l in enumerate(lines):\n    if 'Phase 1 done' in l:\n        p1_done_line = i\n        break\n\nprint(f\"'Phase 1 done' at line {p1_done_line}\")\n\n# Find \"for ep in range(PRETRAIN_EP):\" to add checkpoint load before it\np1_for_line = None\nfor i, l in enumerate(lines):\n    if 'for ep in range(PRETRAIN_EP):' in l:\n        p1_for_line = i\n        break\n\nprint(f\"PRETRAIN_EP for loop at line {p1_for_line}\")\n\n# New lines to ADD before Phase 1 for loop\npre_phase1 = [\n    \"# Checkpointing: skip Phase 1 if checkpoint exists for this seed\\n\",\n    \"PRETRAIN_CKPT = f'/workspace/srmoe_p1_{DEEPSEED}.pt'\\n\",\n    \"if os.path.exists(PRETRAIN_CKPT):\\n\",\n    \"    print(f'Loading Phase 1 checkpoint: {PRETRAIN_CKPT}')\\n\",\n    \"    ckpt = torch.load(PRETRAIN_CKPT, map_location=DEVICE)\\n\",\n    \"    model.load_state_dict(ckpt['model'])\\n\",\n    \"    trainer.opt.load_state_dict(ckpt['optimizer'])\\n\",\n    \"    trainer._ep_count = ckpt.get('ep_count', 0)\\n\",\