{"type":"message","id":"456f92e6","parentId":"030340ce","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:36:58.297Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Backup is at `C:\\dev\\notebooks\\SRMoE_Training_BACKUP_20260324.ipynb`. Now let me add the checkpoint logic to the training cell.\n\nThe plan:\n1. After \"Phase 1 done\" print, save checkpoint: `torch.save({'model': model.state_dict(), 'routing_tau': model.routing.tau, ...}, 'phase1_checkpoint.pt')`\n2. At the START of the training cell (before Phase 1), check if checkpoint exists AND a flag `SKIP_PHASE1` is set\n3. If so: load checkpoint, skip Phase 1, jump to Phase 2\n\n\n4. I'll make it easy to toggle with a simple boolean flag at the top of the cell, so Zach can quickly switch between running Phase 1 fresh or loading from checkpoint.","thinkingSignature":"998761efbe3234b2cb1b51b2aceb1fe7edd819f5bbabcc100de0e17f178efce6"},{"type":"text","text":"Backup at `C:\\dev\\notebooks\\SRMoE_Training_BACKUP_20260324.ipynb`. Now adding the checkpoint logic:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yhz21uofgbou_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport json, sys\nwith open(r'C:\\dev\\notebooks\\SRMoE_Training.ipynb', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f: nb = json.load(f)\nlines = nb['cells'][10]['source']\nprint('Phase 1 loop: lines 9-18')\nfor i in range(9, 20):\n    sys.stdout.write('%3d: %s\\n' % (i, lines[i].encode('ascii','replace').decode()))\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103325,"output":329,"cacheRead":14175,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117829,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774366608024}}
{"type":"message","id":"53bae9fa","parentId":"456f92e6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:36:59.263Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yhz21uofgbou_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Phase 1 loop: lines 9-18\r\n  9: print(f'Phase 1: Supervised pre-training ({PRETRAIN_EP} ep)')\r\n\r\n 10: t0 = time.time()\r\n\r\n 11: for ep in range(PRETRAIN_EP):\r\n\r\n 12:     stats = trainer.train_episode(generate_episode(DEEPSEED + ep), use_oracle_routing=True)\r\n\r\n 13:     if ep % 200 == 0 or ep == PRETRAIN_EP - 1:\r\n\r\n 14:         print(f'  ep {ep:5d}: loss={stats[\"loss\"]:.4f}  acc={stats[\"accuracy\"]:.3f}  '\r\n\r\n 15:               f'route_ce={stats[\"route_loss\"]:.4f}  div={stats[\"div_loss\"]:.4f}  '\r\n\r\n 16:               f'wr={stats[\"write_frac\"]:.2f}  rd={stats[\"read_frac\"]:.2f}  '\r\n\r\n 17:               f'skip={stats[\"skip_frac\"]:.2f}  occ={stats[\"avg_occupancy\"]:.1f}')\r\n\r\n 18: print(f'  Phase 1 done in {time.time()-t0:.0f}s\\n')\r\n\r\n 19:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":812,"aggregated":"Phase 1 loop: lines 9-18\r\n  9: print(f'Phase 1: Supervised pre-training ({PRETRAIN_EP} ep)')\r\n\r\n 10: t0 = time.time()\r\n\r\n 11: for ep in range(PRETRAIN_EP):\r\n\r\n 12:     stats = trainer.train_episode(generate_episode(DEEPSEED + ep), use_oracle_routing=True)\r\n\r\n 13:     if ep % 200 == 0 or ep == PRETRAIN_EP - 1:\r\n\r\n 14:         print(f'  ep {ep:5d}: loss={stats[\"loss\"]:.4f}  acc={stats[\"accuracy\"]:.3f}  '\r\n\r\n 15:               f'route_ce={stats[\"route_loss\"]:.4f}  div={stats[\"div_loss\"]:.4f}  '\r\n\r\n 16:               f'wr={stats[\"write_frac\"]:.2f}  rd={stats[\"read_frac\"]:.2f}  '\r\n\r\n 17:               f'skip={stats[\"skip_frac\"]:.2f}  occ={stats[\"avg_occupancy\"]:.1f}')\r\n\r\n 18: print(f'  Phase 1 done in {time.time()-t0:.0f}s\\n')\r\n\r\n 19:","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774366619175}}
{"type":"message","id":"857ff1bb","parentId":"53bae9fa","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:37:17.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll:\n1. Add `SKIP_PHASE1 = False` and `PHASE1_CKPT = 'phase1_checkpoint.pt'` constants at the top of the training cell\n2. Add checkpoint save after Phase 1 done\n3. Add checkpoint load + skip at the start (before Phase 1 loop)","thinkingSignature":"f419e197653671369800e99ad1b1449ccba59cf3ef1b94d79138fb32d3995052"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sf9ycermuqi8_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\add_checkpoint.py","content":"import json\n\nwith open(r'C:\\dev\\notebooks\\SRMoE_Training.ipynb', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    nb = json.load(f)\n\nlines = nb['cells'][10]['source']\nsrc = ''.join(lines)\n\n# ── 1. Add checkpoint constants after PRETRAIN/HARDEN_EP definitions ──────────\nckpt_const = \"\"\"\n# Checkpoint settings\nSKIP_PHASE1 = False          # True = load phase1 checkpoint and skip Phase 1 training\nPHASE1_CKPT = '/workspace/phase1_checkpoint.pt'  # adjust path for your setup\n\"\"\"\n\n# Find the line after HARDEN_EP definition\ninsert_after_line = None\nfor i, line in enumerate(lines):\n    if 'HARDEN_EP =' in line:\n        insert_after_line = i\n        break\n\nif insert_after_line is not None:\n    new_lines = lines[:insert_after_line+1] + [ckpt_const] + lines[insert_after_line+1:]\n    print(f\"Inserted checkpoint constants after line {insert_after_line}\")\nelse:\n    new_lines = [ckpt_const] + lines\n    print(\"Prepended checkpoint constants\")\n\n# ── 2. Add checkpoint save after Phase 1 done print ────────────────────────────\nsave_after = \"print(f'  Phase 1 done in {time.time()-t0:.0f}s\\\\n')\"\nsave_block = \"\"\"print(f'  Phase 1 done in {time.time()-t0:.0f}s\\\\n')\n\n# Save Phase 1 checkpoint\ntorch.save({\n    'model_state': model.state_dict(),\n    'optimizer_state': trainer.opt.state_dict(),\n    'tau': model.routing.tau if hasattr(model.routing, 'tau') else None,\n    'ep_count': PRETRAIN_EP,\n}, PHASE1_CKPT)\nprint(f'Phase 1 checkpoint saved to {PHASE1_CKPT}\\\\n')\n\"\"\"\n\nnew_src = ''.join(new_lines).replace(save_after, save_block)\nnb['cells'][10]['source'] = [new_src]\n\n# ── 3. Add checkpoint load + skip before Phase 1 loop ─────────────────────────\nskip_block = \"\"\"# Load Phase 1 checkpoint and skip training if configured\nif SKIP_PHASE1 and os.path.exists(PHASE1_CKPT):\n    ckpt = torch.load(PHASE1_CKPT, map_location=DEVICE)\n    model.load_state_dict(ckpt['model_state'])\n    trainer.opt.load_state_dict(ckpt['optimizer_state'])\n    if hasattr(model.routing, '_step'):\n        model.routing._step = ckpt.get('ep_count', PRETRAIN_EP)\n    print(f'Loaded Phase 1 checkpoint from {PHASE1_CKPT} - skipping Phase 1\\\\n')\nelse:\n\"\"\"\n\np1_start_marker = \"print(f'Phase 1: Supervised pre-training\"\nif p1_start_marker in new_src:\n    new_src2 = new_src.replace(p1_start_marker, skip_block + p1_start_marker, 1)\n    print(\"Inserted checkpoint load/skip before Phase 1\")\nelse:\n    print(\"ERROR: could not find Phase 1 start marker\")\n    new_src2 = new_src\n\nnb['cells'][10]['source'] = [new_src2]\n\nwith open(r'C:\\dev\\notebooks\\SRMoE_Training.ipynb', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    json.dump(nb, f, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(\"Checkpoint logic added. Saved.\")\nprint()\nprint(\"Usage:\")\nprint(\"  SKIP_PHASE1 = False  -> run Phase 1 normally (fresh training)\")\nprint(\"  SKIP_PHASE1 = True   -> load checkpoint and jump to Phase 2\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103952,"output":920,"cacheRead":14175,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119047,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774366619269}}
