{"type":"message","id":"356aeb92","parentId":"7a3b1948","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:16:56.257Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The backup restored the state BEFORE we added checkpointing. So `SKIP_PHASE1` is not in the notebook yet. I need to add the checkpoint logic from scratch.\n\nBut also I see the backup is the state with the DAgger fix but without checkpointing. Let me just add the minimal checkpoint logic.\n\nPlan:\n1. Add SKIP_PHASE1 = False and PHASE1_CKPT = None after HARDEN_EP = 2000 (after line 7)\n2. Add the if/else block before Phase 1 (before line 9)\n3. Add checkpoint save after Phase 1 done (after line 18)4. \nChange PHASE1_CKPT = None to guard the save\n\nSince Paperspace free tier doesn't have persistent storage, I'll disable checkpointing and just let Phase 1 run fresh each time. This means SKIP_PHASE1 = False and PHASE1_CKPT = None, so the checkpoint logic just becomes a no-op.\n\nNow I need to implement this cleanly by inserting the checkpoint variables and conditional logic into the notebook at the right locations, with PHASE1_CKPT = None to prevent any actual file writes.","thinkingSignature":"f74ebf9973c57a2b975c5500e81e318ffc3518c5c49af08ffee199564b3c02c2"},{"type":"text","text":"Good — backup restored cleanly. Now adding checkpoint logic carefully as a new cell rather than patching the existing training cell:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jaikajahao0c_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\add_ckpt.py","content":"import json\n\nwith open(r'C:\\dev\\notebooks\\SRMoE_Training.ipynb', 'r', encoding='utf-8', errors='replace') as f:\n    nb = json.load(f)\n\n# ── New cell: checkpoint configuration (insert as cell 10, before training cell) ─\n# This way we don't touch the training cell structure at all\n\nckpt_cell_lines = [\n    \"# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\\n\",\n    \"# Phase 1 Checkpoint Settings\\n\",\n    \"#\\n\",\n    \"# To skip Phase 1 after first run: set SKIP_PHASE1 = True and ensure\\n\",\n    \"# PHASE1_CKPT points to a valid checkpoint file (e.g. on Google Drive).\\n\",\n    \"# On Paperspace free tier: keep SKIP_PHASE1 = False (no persistent storage).\\n\",\n    \"# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"SKIP_PHASE1 = False          # True = load checkpoint and skip Phase 1\\n\",\n    \"PHASE1_CKPT = None           # set to '/workspace/phase1_checkpoint.pt' for persistent storage\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"# Load checkpoint and skip Phase 1 if configured\\n\",\n    \"if SKIP_PHASE1 and PHASE1_CKPT is not None:\\n\",\n    \"    import os\\n\",\n    \"    if os.path.exists(PHASE1_CKPT):\\n\",\n    \"        ckpt = torch.load(PHASE1_CKPT, map_location=DEVICE)\\n\",\n    \"        model.load_state_dict(ckpt['model_state'])\\n\",\n    \"        trainer.opt.load_state_dict(ckpt['optimizer_state'])\\n\",\n    \"        if hasattr(model.routing, '_step'):\\n\",\n    \"            model.routing._step = ckpt.get('ep_count', PRETRAIN_EP)\\n\",\n    \"        print(f'Loaded Phase 1 checkpoint - skipping Phase 1\\\\n')\\n\",\n    \"    else:\\n\",\n    \"        print(f'WARNING: checkpoint {PHASE1_CKPT} not found, running Phase 1 normally\\\\n')\\n\",\n    \"        SKIP_PHASE1 = False  # force run Phase 1\\n\",\n    \"elif SKIP_PHASE1:\\n\",\n    \"    print('WARNING: PHASE1_CKPT is None, cannot skip Phase 1\\\\n')\\n\",\n    \"    SKIP_PHASE1 = False\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"# ── Phase 1 (controlled by SKIP_PHASE1) ───────────────────────────────────\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"if not SKIP_PHASE1:\\n\",\n    \"    print(f'Phase 1: Supervised pre-training ({PRETRAIN_EP} ep)')\\n\",\n    \"    t0 = time.time()\\n\",\n    \"    for ep in range(PRETRAIN_EP):\\n\",\n    \"        stats = trainer.train_episode(generate_episode(DEEPSEED + ep), use_oracle_routing=True)\\n\",\n    \"        if ep % 200 == 0 or ep == PRETRAIN_EP - 1:\\n\",\n    \"            print(f'  ep {ep:5d}: loss={stats[\\\"loss\\\"]:.4f}  acc={stats[\\\"accuracy\\\"]:.3f}  '\\n\",\n    \"                  f'route_ce={stats[\\\"route_loss\\\"]:.4f}  div={stats[\\\"div_loss\\\"]:.4f}  '\\n\",\n    \"                  f'wr={stats[\\\"write_frac\\\"]:.2f}  rd={stats[\\\"read_frac\\\"]:.2f}  '\\n\",\n    \"                  f'skip={stats[\\\"skip_frac\\\"]:.2f}  occ={stats[\\\"avg_occupancy\\\"]:.1f}')\\n\",\n    \"    print(f'  Phase 1 done in {time.time()-t0:.0f}s\\\\n')\\n\",\n    \"    if PHASE1_CKPT is not None:\\n\",\n    \"        torch.save({\\n\",\n    \"            'model_state': model.state_dict(),\\n\",\n    \"            'optimizer_state': trainer.opt.state_dict(),\\n\",\n    \"            'tau': model.routing.tau if hasattr(model.routing, 'tau') else None,\\n\",\n    \"            'ep_count': PRETRAIN_EP,\\n\",\n    \"        }, PHASE1_CKPT)\\n\",\n    \"        print(f'Phase 1 checkpoint saved to {PHASE1_CKPT}\\\\n')\\n\",\n    \"else:\\n\",\n    \"    print(f'Phase 1: SKIPPED (checkpoint loaded)\\\\n')\\n\",\n]\n\nckpt_cell = {\n    \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n    \"execution_count\": None,\n    \"id\": \"checkpoint-cell\",\n    \"metadata\": {},\n    \"outputs\": [],\n    \"source\": ckpt_cell_lines\n}\n\n# Insert as cell 10 (0-based), shifting the old training cell to 11\nnb['cells'].insert(10, ckpt_cell)\nprint(f\"Inserted checkpoint cell at position 10. Total cells: {len(nb['cells'])}\")\n\nwith open(r'C:\\dev\\notebooks\\SRMoE_Training.ipynb', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    json.dump(nb, f, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(\"Saved. Checkpoint cell inserted — Phase 1 training now controlled by SKIP_PHASE1 flag.\")\nprint(\"SKIP_PHASE1 = False (default): Phase 1 runs normally\")\nprint(\"SKIP_PHASE1 = True + PHASE1_CKPT set: loads checkpoint, skips Phase 1\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107221,"output":1564,"cac